data.description: ***INVESTOR'S ONLY*** Welcome to Misty Lake, Ellenwood GA! This home offers a great opportunity for INVESTORS seeking lucrative returns. Just minutes away from Fork Creek Mountain Park, this property has amazing potential.  5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms all on 3795 SQFT. The home has a 2 story foyer, two primary suites (one on main) Private Deck, Spacious primary bathroom with separate Tub and shower. Kitchen has ample cabinet space. The upper level holds 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Lower level has another primary bedroom, and another living space, with bathroom. Half bathroom is on main level. This property is being sold AS IS, interior work is needed. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
